  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TPa14">
<l>uṅkaḷ puḻaikkaṭait tōṭṭattu vāviyuḷ</l>
<l>ceṅkaḻuṉīr vāy nekiḻntāmpal vāy kūmpiṉa kāṇ</l>
<l>ceṅkaṟ poṭik kūṟai veṇpal tavattavar</l>
<l>taṅkaḷ tirukkōyil caṅkiṭuvāṉ pōkiṉṟār</l>
<l>eṅkaḷai muṉṉam eḻuppuvāṉ vāypēcum</l>
<l>naṅkāy eḻuntirāy nāṇātāy nāvuṭaiyāy</l>
<l>caṅkōṭu cakkaram ēntum taṭakkaiyaṉ</l>
<l>paṅkayak kaṇṇāṉaip pāṭēlōr empāvāy.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Inside the well of your backyard garden,</l>
<l>the ceṅkaḻunīr-flowers have opened up,</l>
<l>and the water-lilies have closed, see!</l>
<l>The white-toothed ascetics with clothes [the hue of] brick dust</l>
<l>are going to blow the conch of their sacred temple.</l>
<l>O lady who said you would wake us up first!</l>
<l>Get up, O shameless [girl], who have [the gift of] the gab!</l>
<l>Sing [about]</l>
<l rend="indent">Him with lotus eyes [and] big arms</l>
<l rend="indent">who holds the discus along with the conch.</l>
<l>O our maidens, accept [and] consider [this] attentively!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
